sorcer.core.provider.cataloger.ui

Class SignatureDispatcherForCataloger

  • java.lang.Object
    • sorcer.core.provider.cataloger.ui.SignatureDispatcherForCataloger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener, SignatureDispatchment

    public class SignatureDispatcherForCataloger
extends java.lang.Object
implements SignatureDispatchment
    Implementation of the SignatureDispatcherInterface to provide support for using Cataloger as a data source. This implementation calls Cataloger to obtain most of the information that it needs. This version is utilized for the Cataloger UI.
